<div class="loginWrap">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="panel margin-bottom-0">
            <div class="panel-heading header">
                <div class="panel-title "><img src="../../images/login/line.png">找回密码</div>
            </div>
            <form class="panel-body text-center">
                <ul class="list-inline row step">
                    <li>
                        <ul class="list-inline">
                            <li class="hexagon"><img src="../../images/login/hexagon.png"/><p>1</p></li>
                            <li class="stepActive">验证手机号</li>
                            <li class="line"></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <ul class="list-inline">
                            <li class="hexagon"><img src="../../images/login/hexagon.png"/><p>2</p></li>
                            <li class="stepActive">输入新密码</li>
                            <li class="line"></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <ul class="list-inline">
                            <li class="hexagon"><img src="../../images/login/hexagon.png"/><p>3</p></li>
                            <li class="stepActive">完成</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div>
                    <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-2">
                        <div class="prompt">
                            <p><div><img src="../../images/success.png"></div>
                            恭喜您，登陆密码找回成功！<span>{{time}}s</span>后自动转跳至登陆页</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="margin-bottom-198">
                            <button class="btn btn-warning col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-xs-8 radius-0
                                           col-md-offset-2 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-offset-2" ui-sref="app.login({loginMod:1})">立即登陆</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>